All tracks are ~160kbps. Painstakingly tagged and organized. Some tracks have been remastered by me and some tracks that are meant to flow together have been combined by me.

One stop shop for most, if not all, of your emo needs. Over 100 hours. Everything from Midwest emo to emo pop to screamo to emoviolence

This is a single .zip file because there are too many files to upload otherwise, sorry for any inconvenience caused by not being able to select/deselect files.
